scm-support-plugin.title: Support
scm-support-plugin.subtitle: Gather support information for this SCM-Manager instance

collect.help: Will give you everything you need to know and even more.

trace.help: Switch logging to trace level and gather a lot of logs for a limited time. To do this, enable the trace. You will get the logs when you switch it off again.
trace.warning: Please keep in mind, that this may slow down this instance!
